description: Gets an Amazon DataZone data source run.

parameters.name: domainIdentifier
parameters.description: The ID of the domain in which this data source run was performed.

parameters.name: identifier
parameters.description: The ID of the data source run.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when the data source run was created.

nested_items.name: dataSourceConfigurationSnapshot
nested_items.description: The configuration snapshot of the data source run.

nested_items.name: dataSourceId
nested_items.description: The ID of the data source for this data source run.

nested_items.name: domainId
nested_items.description: The ID of the domain in which this data source run was performed.

nested_items.name: errorMessage
nested_items.description: Specifies the error message that is returned if the operation cannot be successfully completed.

nested_items.name: errorDetail
nested_items.description: The details of the error message that is returned if the operation cannot be successfully completed.

nested_items.name: errorType
nested_items.description: The type of the error message that is returned if the operation cannot be successfully completed.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The ID of the data source run.

nested_items.name: lineageSummary
nested_items.description: The summary of the data lineage.

nested_items.name: importStatus
nested_items.description: The import status that's part of the run lineage summary of a data source.

nested_items.name: projectId
nested_items.description: The ID of the project in which this data source run occured.

nested_items.name: runStatisticsForAssets
nested_items.description: The asset statistics from this data source run.

nested_items.name: added
nested_items.description: The added statistic for the data source run.

nested_items.name: failed
nested_items.description: The failed statistic for the data source run.

nested_items.name: skipped
nested_items.description: The skipped statistic for the data source run.

nested_items.name: unchanged
nested_items.description: The unchanged statistic for the data source run.

nested_items.name: updated
nested_items.description: The updated statistic for the data source run.

nested_items.name: startedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when this data source run started.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of this data source run.

nested_items.name: stoppedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when this data source run stopped.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: The type of this data source run.

nested_items.name: updatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp of when this data source run was updated.
